{"tid":1677002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"痴線！點解仲會有人自己一個番屋企","createTime":"2019-10-26T19:38:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T04:34:13.000Z","uid":63456,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e5cca06a2d4afe3af5c9dec0da4eacb8e0c85b1c","tid":1677002,"uid":63456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T19:38:03.000Z","msg":"無錯個個就係我朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n代Po<br />\n<br />\n我係今日係元朗比2個廢佬打嘅細佬<br />\n出呢個Po係想多謝救咗我嘅FA哥哥<br />\n<br />\n事源呢 因為行街行太夜啦 <br />\n之後我自己一個行返屋企<br />\n買完嘢飲之後<br />\n無啦啦比兩個廢佬追住打 <br />\n打咗幾拳<br />\n個頭有D暈暈地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩有個FA哥哥係對面馬路跑過嚟捉住我走<br />\n如果唔係我可能唔只係爛眼鏡<br />\n可能入咗醫院<br />\n<br />\n多謝你FA哥哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有記住唔好自己一個返屋企ar<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3點尖沙咀見啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"ac8e94732d648887540ddb3dfa7edbcf901b321f","tid":1677002,"uid":63456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T19:39:00.000Z","msg":"自推十連 1"},{"pid":"50f1bc9f0d88d42253cb432850c05a9099201309","tid":1677002,"uid":63456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T19:39:17.000Z","msg":"二推"},{"pid":"b4ec6835b71f4dc4934de4b4928a47384c7d53d0","tid":1677002,"uid":63456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T19:39:27.000Z","msg":"三推"},{"pid":"8ae132d321266e109f4689886a6bf5ff7dd0e5a5","tid":1677002,"uid":63456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T19:39:40.